<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3682] Wrong value stored for a radio button with an /Opts entry</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3682</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a radio button has an &lt;tt&gt;/Opts&lt;/tt&gt; entry PDFBox saves the index of the value in the &lt;tt&gt;/Opts&lt;/tt&gt; array as the fields value in &lt;tt&gt;/V&lt;/tt&gt; instead of the appearance entries name for the &lt;tt&gt;On&lt;/tt&gt; state the index is pointing to.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13042378">PDFBOX-3682</key>
            <summary>Wrong value stored for a radio button with an /Opts entry</summary>
